{"tid":1104143,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"過期奶精16噸 再製奶茶銷183店","createTime":"2019-04-13T02:19:17.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-13T02:57:36.000Z","uid":56561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"df6022bbbc5aa113ae93f76591fd51504481e442","tid":1104143,"uid":56561,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T02:19:17.000Z","msg":"又見黑心奶精！高市衛生局會同檢警查獲位於岡山34年老字號「伯享生技」，涉嫌將逾期或即期奶精，再製奶茶、咖啡等31項產品，數量超過16.39噸，粗查產品賣到高雄、台南、屏東的早餐店、小吃店逾183家，奶精最久逾期近1年，民眾恐怕早已吃下肚，衛生局已要求勒令歇業並下架回收。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.chinatimes.com/newspapers/20190413000539-260106\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.chinatimes.com%2Fnewspapers%2F20190413000539-260106&d=UVXHPnZi3uDb3BtvOfiAhGt2mj8CN1oGBszRVJtr96Q%3D&h=13190506\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.chinatimes.com/newspapers/20190413000539-260106</a><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n到底呢種劣質飲食文化點先可以絕跡？"},{"pid":"ad31b0aa90c2a42e6368369faf90b496b409ceb5","tid":1104143,"uid":987,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T02:26:57.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"592c6703bc1867223e5d9ff013329aa7ad9e34bf","tid":1104143,"uid":162713,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-04-13T02:30:01.000Z","msg":"台灣早餐店奶茶不嬲都飲到人肚痾<br />\n起士蛋餅 大冰奶<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angel.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n去親台灣都飲番兩杯 清腸胃<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c51668bbe11c4f2acee869df58f17d55d51be314","tid":1104143,"uid":45368,"like":